room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Milwaukee in Milwaukee
review: We didn't win, but we sure had a great time! The Agency room is not for the faint of heart. I recommend a group of 6-8 for this super fun experience.

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Milwaukee in Milwaukee
review: Went with some friends last night and we had a lot of fun! We did the agency room, and it was very cool! Props and furniture were very cool and high quality! Lots of interesting props and puzzles made it a truly unique and exciting experience! I would highly recommend it!

room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Escape the Room Milwaukee in Milwaukee
review: Had a blast in the Agency Room! Soooo close! Definitely worth checking out! Can't wait to go back and check out thr other rooms!
